00:37:19.077 --> 00:37:20.660
probably going to
win with a straight,

00:37:20.660 --> 00:37:22.659
although not all
the time, because he

00:37:22.659 --> 00:37:23.950
doesn't have the best straight.

00:37:23.950 --> 00:37:26.430
If a nine comes
and then this guy

00:37:26.430 --> 00:37:31.590
has queen, king-- or
sorry, jack, queen,

00:37:31.590 --> 00:37:34.422
he's going to actually lose.

00:37:34.422 --> 00:37:36.130
So the question is,
