00:38:14.660 --> 00:38:16.226
get to see?

00:38:16.226 --> 00:38:18.350
AUDIENCE: Why 10 and
1/2? [INAUDIBLE].

00:38:18.350 --> 00:38:22.030
PROFESSOR: Because you can
