00:38:31.460 --> 00:38:33.880
So I'm not really comfortable
calling those complete outs,

00:38:33.880 --> 00:38:36.750
and in the end, you can see
it doesn't really matter.

00:38:36.750 --> 00:38:38.510
But the more
conservative move is just

00:38:38.510 --> 00:38:40.790
saying half the time
we'll win with those,

00:38:40.790 --> 00:38:43.620
and with these nine outs we're
going to win all the time.

00:38:43.620 --> 00:38:45.230
You can just count
them as half outs,

00:38:45.230 --> 00:38:49.310
or you can count them as 2/3
outs, or something like that.

00:38:49.310 --> 00:38:51.760
Anyway, so we get to see both
cards because he's all in.

00:38:51.760 --> 00:38:52.610
You have a question?

00:38:52.610 --> 00:38:55.514
AUDIENCE: This would
