00:40:19.340 --> 00:40:22.710
so that's dead money in the pot.

00:40:22.710 --> 00:40:25.090
So the total amount
is $14,450, and we're

00:40:25.090 --> 00:40:31.180
facing a bet of $4525, so 31%
of the pot we're contributing.

00:40:31.180 --> 00:40:33.920
We're 42% to hit our
draws, meaning that this

00:40:33.920 --> 00:40:35.290
is a pretty clear call.

00:40:35.290 --> 00:40:40.590
And when we do the EV, even
with this conservative estimate,

00:40:40.590 --> 00:40:44.380
it says we're making
about $1.5 million chips

00:40:44.380 --> 00:40:45.620
for making this call.

00:40:45.620 --> 00:40:47.410
So this should be pretty easy.

00:40:47.410 --> 00:40:49.668
Let's see what happens, and
let's see if this works.

